OL,4,Cnow visible in night sky
OL,6,FStuart Atkinson, an amateur astronomer
OL,7,Fbased in Cumbria, has been tracking
OL,8,Fthe object for some time, taking
OL,9,Fphotos on his Canon 700D DSLR camera.
OL,11,FHe said that, technically, 12P/Pons-
OL,12,FBrooks should be visible to the naked
OL,13,Feye now but "in reality, it needs a
OL,14,Fpair of binoculars or a telescope to
OL,15,Fbe seen because most people live in
OL,16,Fplaces with light pollution".
